ortunities to make money. Channels are not to save money, but to use your only money to buy opportunities and to test. Living within your means is the thinking of the poor, and the rich even have the thinking of borrowing money. Thinking of payment. The poor have been saving, and the result is getting poorer and poorer.\\n\\nWhen a rich man does business, he sells experience, while a rich man is already rich in material things. What he is willing to buy is experience and spiritual things. Therefore, I suggest that those who want to make a lot of money sell spiritual things. For example, education, training, look at the most profitable businesses, such as Disney, such as the game field, such as the current anchors, gun scheduling tools, in fact, are spiritual products, low cost, and extremely profitable.\\n\\nYou cannot be romantic without money. Romance has a price. If you can create romance, you will make money. Smart boss, only chat with excellent colleagues, assign tasks to make excellent\\n\\nPeople to finish. In everything, you must develop the habit of proactively tracking and checking. You leave one thing to\\n\\nThe employee does it. If you don’t follow up, he may not do it or mess up. The boss must learn to guide and track employees. We will expel all those who are not good, and increase recruitment. The company has excellent people, and the performance will naturally go up. Implement the last elimination system to form a competition mechanism. When funds permit, scale up quickly.\\n\\nWhen there are people, all kinds of things are easy to handle. People in the company must be rich. There are more people and more power, but there are fewer people. Everyone thinks that they are awesome. People who are not so capable are also showing off in front of the boss. To form the idea and facts that the company can operate well without anyone else.\\n\\nSaving is the biggest waste. Ideas that the poor think are right often hinder their success\\n\\nEntrepreneur Business School Serving Entrepreneurs 191\\n\\nConcept. If you don't understand, even if you work hard, you can only be poor. Saving will make people lose morale, have a narrow mind, and see no opportunity or opportunity.\\n\\nYes, it will keep the wealthy away from him. The employees or consultants you hire, if they can’t teach you smarter, or you order\\n\\nThey always make excuses for things, so they fire him. Don't be soft. What a kind-hearted heart greeted us was just getting worse.\\n\\nRespect your own time, people respect themselves, only then they have value, have status, and have a future. Others have to respect you. Respect is won by strength, not by expecting others to be polite and quality. high. Respect is because others dare not disrespect you. Caesar said that instead of letting others love you, it is better to let others be afraid of you. Love you, respect you, and betray you. And fear is the ultimate weapon of the winner.\",\"timestamp\":1634801117,\"title\":\"Evil bosses can run a good business\"},\"digest\":\"HCepRVyew172B9JzxgraaUyQCHSdiOc6IGn_ZlogC-A\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0500e3b6f7b1214a11851b9B348020C08018403b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"xgLgYwMjJiK-aV2S2HksdtePHeBe7nclcpqYjlzvw7CPyK3nGER_yYb3aZlNlywZ435sdwCsXibeKGpkKtJN5A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1c6f856baad7dbcdc04a289cfb8c27fd2d4c254469eae7a6d5e283ce19250e091ab85676074d27b49e23c7d4b78b5f81e8536a0da448b30920c0f4dc5a6602e41c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"nKf8ZamRyX8cLVb8DeIErgOMrQgMun7f02Hq_yDPgjE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3htkpr16jLLCk2n5vgcjMXkGx9Ypl9sCU0ngm5GUXu8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\